14	pleasanton-cottage-kitchen	Pleasanton Cottage Kitchen	Pleasanton	Kitchen Remodel	2021	A cottage-style kitchen remodel in Pleasanton that leans into charm without sacrificing function — shaker cabinetry, classic hardware, and a layout designed around how the family actually lives.	\N	\N	/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_f575a25ba7f14e1389d0ae63bb2d356f_mv2.webp	{/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_9a3cb5be52fb466ebd047a075c89ee74_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_f575a25ba7f14e1389d0ae63bb2d356f_mv2.webp}	t	14	2026-03-31 02:25:34.606122+00	2026-04-04 05:03:29.997119+00	CA	kitchen-bath	A cottage-style kitchen remodel in Pleasanton that leans into charm without sacrificing function — shaker cabinetry, classic hardware, and a layout designed around how the family actually lives.	Sometimes a kitchen doesn't need to make a bold statement — it just needs to be perfect. The Pleasanton Cottage Kitchen is exactly that: a beautifully resolved remodel that feels at home in a cottage-style residence without ever feeling small or dated.\n\nShaker-style cabinetry in a warm white finish, classic hardware, and a thoughtfully designed layout create a kitchen that's as functional as it is charming. Every storage decision was deliberate — maximizing usable space while keeping the aesthetic clean and inviting.\n\nRidgecrest Designs produced full photo-realistic renders before breaking ground, giving the clients complete confidence in every material choice before the first cabinet was installed.	{"What":"Kitchen Remodel","Where":"Pleasanton, CA","When":"2021"}	ff5b18_f575a25ba7f14e1389d0ae63bb2d356f_mv2	png	[["ff5b18_9a3cb5be52fb466ebd047a075c89ee74_mv2", "png"], ["ff5b18_f575a25ba7f14e1389d0ae63bb2d356f_mv2", "png"], ["ff5b18_56956b7fa72d450998718343281c35e4_mv2", "webp"], ["ff5b18_c5cb0ea7b12844efb50e924af0d95a33_mv2", "webp"]]	f
4	danville-hilltop	Danville Hilltop	Danville	Kitchen Remodel	2020	A mid-century hilltop kitchen at the top of Eugene O'Neill National Historic Park, reimagined with custom cabinetry, hand-fabricated steel wall storage, and an iconic blue-and-walnut contrast that turns heads.	\N	\N	/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_598ba1466dbb45249778e2ea0e0b95e3_mv2.webp	{/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_4a378f6899d24b5ba7bc7551ea53540a_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_c0e8f9e9008c498eac5efafae3c46b04_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_1ef4108f78534aa59c515d38946c4644_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_b246a630ba864e2a8fe67d964745b9b5_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_7e0f0e5602694ed280e46ec708e7b068_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_63757c728db94733b4f60a7102c0f722_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_487bdc0f0af642d9b49405d476c80c5e_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_7bdab37a61b24537af57e91ce2978f4c_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_b0f0c5eecc8d4f7ba7ae030a334d5f93_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_19b678ef0cf34b9ca705133688ea91b1_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_10521de8c90243f58322ebef9335a4c8_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_864272d4755d468096cd4e388a01a773_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_5ed3b0005abb494885a58ee0c4508248_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_b93571ff11674224b7489b5e425116ee_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_c520c9ca384d4c3ebe02707d0c8f45ab_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_33d2068cd10941fbad0293bdc73d63d5_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_4e56d06b0c6e4c80aabe636642bf8346_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_cd0bbd1ca0924ba38e0578501a1958ec_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_598ba1466dbb45249778e2ea0e0b95e3_mv2.webp}	t	4	2026-03-31 02:25:34.606122+00	2026-04-04 05:03:27.803507+00	CA	kitchen-bath	A mid-century hilltop kitchen at the top of Eugene O'Neill National Historic Park, reimagined with custom cabinetry, hand-fabricated steel wall storage, and an iconic blue-and-walnut contrast that turns heads.	Situated at the top of the Eugene O'Neill National Historic Park in Danville, this mid-century modern hilltop home had great architectural features, but needed a kitchen update that spoke to the design style of the rest of the house. We would have to say this project was one of our most challenging when it came to blending the mid-century style of the house with an eclectic and modern look that the clients were drawn to. But, who doesn't love a good challenge?\n\nWe removed the builder-grade cabinetry put in by a previous owner and took down a wall to open up the kitchen to the rest of the great room. The kitchen features a custom designed hood as well as custom cabinetry with an intricate beaded detail, setting it apart from all other cabinetry designs.\n\nThe pop of blue paired with the dark walnut creates an eye-catching contrast. Ridgecrest also designed and fabricated solid steel wall cabinetry to store countertop appliances and display dishes and glasses. The copper accents on the range and faucets bring the design full circle and finish this gorgeous one-of-a-kind kitchen.	{"What":"Kitchen Remodel","Where":"Danville, CA","When":"2020"}	ff5b18_598ba1466dbb45249778e2ea0e0b95e3_mv2	jpg	[["ff5b18_4a378f6899d24b5ba7bc7551ea53540a_mv2", "png"], ["ff5b18_b246a630ba864e2a8fe67d964745b9b5_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_7e0f0e5602694ed280e46ec708e7b068_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_63757c728db94733b4f60a7102c0f722_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_487bdc0f0af642d9b49405d476c80c5e_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_c520c9ca384d4c3ebe02707d0c8f45ab_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_598ba1466dbb45249778e2ea0e0b95e3_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_c0e8f9e9008c498eac5efafae3c46b04_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_1ef4108f78534aa59c515d38946c4644_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_33d2068cd10941fbad0293bdc73d63d5_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_4e56d06b0c6e4c80aabe636642bf8346_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_cd0bbd1ca0924ba38e0578501a1958ec_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_7bdab37a61b24537af57e91ce2978f4c_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_b0f0c5eecc8d4f7ba7ae030a334d5f93_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_19b678ef0cf34b9ca705133688ea91b1_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_10521de