10	lafayette-bistro	Lafayette Bistro	Lafayette	Kitchen Remodel	2024	A cramped Lafayette kitchen transformed into a bright, modern bistro-style culinary space — custom cabinetry, white oak finishes, and an open floor plan designed for both daily life and entertaining.	\N	\N	/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_76c5e504c9114ef09ad8233549a16b39_mv2.webp	{/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_1012816bc1d7431cbdba88c8a138d06d_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_62872dfca32e4164a0aae5c292352ece_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_5d2794ad0a8c491484471454087410bb_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_3e1808f4f0464106ae1905f8723d25d3_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_d7eb886d364544c1993777e2db5e8bb6_mv2.webp,/assets/images-opt/ff5b18_76c5e504c9114ef09ad8233549a16b39_mv2.webp}	t	10	2026-03-31 02:25:34.606122+00	2026-04-04 05:03:29.101244+00	CA	kitchen-bath	A cramped Lafayette kitchen transformed into a bright, modern bistro-style culinary space — custom cabinetry, white oak finishes, and an open floor plan designed for both daily life and entertaining.	Ridgecrest Designs transformed a cramped Lafayette kitchen into a bright, modern bistro-style culinary space with custom cabinetry and high-end finishes. The project began — like all Ridgecrest projects — with photo-realistic renders that let the clients see exactly what they were getting before demolition started.\n\nThe open floor plan was created by removing a non-structural wall, flooding the space with natural light and creating a flow between the kitchen and living areas. White oak accents, integrated appliances, and a custom range hood bring warmth and precision to the space.\n\nThe result is a kitchen that functions as the heart of the home — equally suited for a quiet weeknight dinner or a full dinner party.	{"What":"Kitchen Remodel","Where":"Lafayette, CA","When":"2024"}	ff5b18_76c5e504c9114ef09ad8233549a16b39_mv2	jpg	[["ff5b18_62872dfca32e4164a0aae5c292352ece_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_5d2794ad0a8c491484471454087410bb_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_3e1808f4f0464106ae1905f8723d25d3_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_76c5e504c9114ef09ad8233549a16b39_mv2", "jpg"], ["ff5b18_1012816bc1d7431cbdba88c8a138d06d_mv2", "jpg"]]	f
